### Summary
This documentation explains how to deploy and analyze recommendations in personalization campaigns using Amplitude's Profile API. It details the API integration process, including authentication, request parameters, response interpretation, and implementation steps, as well as how to analyze recommendation performance through the Performance tab metrics like lift, conversion rates, and statistical significance.

